{"tid":1368771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我重申一次 27/7係唔主動出擊 但比人搞就要自衛還擊","createTime":"2019-07-26T14:24:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T16:26:19.000Z","uid":12354,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"d7684bc60e059f31d34b919794b4ea1ab75749a5","tid":1368771,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:24:38.000Z","msg":"出面唔知做乜鳩咁撚多罵戰分化Post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又屌人左膠 又屌人大台 乜乜柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我明大家係唔想重蹈雨傘覆徹，但<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地唔係要同勇武割蓆！</span><br />\n<br />\n大家要搞清楚，聽日要和理非唔係指打不還手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">比人打，絕對係要自衛還擊，千祈唔好任打唔嬲。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但元朗並冇衝擊意義，所以希望大家可以和理非咁去元朗食老婆餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</div>"},{"pid":"d4ec7c751d1dd7f05e82d8879752bf58ca8a71ff","tid":1368771,"uid":250023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:25:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a7e04b87970868f0ac6660bb9377943b6f448219","tid":1368771,"uid":271051,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:25:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">推<br />\n同埋唔可以無差別傷人</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0b07dad9cde0d4983ca63c24d12ce161549e19a5","tid":1368771,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:26:00.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"0b1751b11f649ea37f2a18bcbf4376c3cba2cdc6","tid":1368771,"uid":12354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"排版柒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73eb88174c09226f20c70c926d89dce94419a2b0","tid":1368771,"uid":15529