cYKAN0XV833ZjHwxWu4XY82PzypubZpwq4ToZ8-e7M</a>"},{"pid":"cfcaeeadc58ad82014f29ae8cb7bede20cfb3150","tid":1368771,"uid":164851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:31:32.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n大家唔好再鬧交喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇人話打不還手啊<br />\n只係話唔好主動入村打人<br />\n<br />\n我相信前線勇武嘅決定<br />\n亦都明白和理非都係想件事好<br />\n大家有咩好好傾<br />\n唔好俾分化撚乘虛而入啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd0e0fd51799d0534fad56b5397c58f7192caab","tid":1368771,"uid":258098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:31:33.000Z","msg":"有好多兄弟買左迪卡儂 <br />\n但唔記得所有產品入面有RFID！<br />\n<br />\n記得剪牌<br />\n記得剪牌<br />\n記得剪牌"},{"pid":"71907673e37a76c28f0ea669d9c3a68d5aff64ee","tid":1368771,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"食老婆餅喇喂"},{"pid":"159b8e9e7efd90ec2c6dafc6f19cda922a012e4c","tid":1368771,"uid":66113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:32:59.000Z","msg":"不入村 不開波 對家郁手會還拖"},{"pid":"dac77973e8a52b9d9337ca7d88a389824e2ab8e7","tid":1368771,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"拉入人群<br />\n開遮<br />\n做野"},{"pid":"e36c94b23915b418e3237b07691671e17a0d8c97","tid":1368771,"uid":47509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:33:34.000Z","msg":"推 勇武手足智勇雙全"},{"pid":"79a067661d696d1a6beeaeee53cf9fbbd1c1c970","tid":1368771,"uid":186811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:34:00.000Z","msg":"推呀！團結"},{"pid":"6760f7e7001139bb648d976d58e1b889ad24ff31","tid":1368771,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:37:10.000Z","msg":"食老婆餅喇喂"},{"pid":"5e011bf09116268b1238d413994f31cac8b0e6cc","tid":1368771,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:38:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b39a835c2db14b761b2